My earlier two interviews (02 and 03) drifted into a different problem (dorm coordination) and I should not have let them. The team had committed to a specific ICP and a specific problem in Lab 2, and my job in Lab 3-4 was to test that, not to explore adjacent problems. This interview brought me back. I am noting it here so the team can see the course-correction.

**What to do differently next time:**
